(1735, 36, 'page_module_2_content', '<h2>THE APIDAE EXPERIENCE</h2>\r\nAt Apidae, it’s all about how little moments make life big.\r\nThe way we talk to our children becomes their inner voice.\r\nThe objects we curate around our children will become their backdrop of memories.\r\n\r\nWe provide a safe sharing space where growing families\r\ngain the tools and knowledge to thrive in a world of overwhelming choice.\r\nWe suggest products that will be relevant to your family and curated for your baby or child\'s age and stage.\r\n\r\nWhether you’re a parent-to-be, a mum or dad, a close relative, or a friend of a family that is expecting,\r\nwe are happy to help you take the guesswork out of selecting baby essentials.\r\nVisit our showroom, sit down with our experts and explore our exclusive products and specially curated brands.'),
