(2101, 275, 'page_module_1_content', '<em>Mother\'s sweet gentle voice. Father\'s firm embrace. The day I made my first toothless smile or the very first time we stepped out as a family of three.</em>\r\n\r\nNot to mention all the birthdays and other celebrations. But sometimes it\'s life\'s big little moments that mean the absolute most. See how apidae has prepared for , captured, and treasured all those little landmarks of life.\r\n\r\n<a href="#">EXPLORE OUT MILESTONES</a>'),
