(2437, 278, 'page_module_7_content_right', '<h3><strong>4-8 MONTHS</strong>\r\nSitting Up Independently</h3>\r\nAnd all of a sudden, your baby has a new perspective on the world – with that also comes a little bit more independence. Tummy time will have strengthened his neck, back and stomach, allowing him to make this remarkable achievement.\r\n\r\nNow that he can sit independently, leaving his hands free to explore, what will be the first thing he reaches for? After your baby accomplishes this milestone, crawling is right around the corner! Exciting times are ahead.'),
(2438, 278, '_page_module_7_content_right', 'field_5c867582a11f1'),
(2439, 278, 'page_module_8_anchor_text', '1 - 2 YEARS'),
(2440, 278, '_page_module_8_anchor_text', 'field_5c86767726493'),
