(2707, 290, 'page_module_4_content_left', '<h3><strong>3 MONTHS</strong>\r\nFirst Holiday</h3>\r\nIgniting the love of travel is one of the best gifts you can give your children. That innate wanderlust will one day develop into countless beautiful memories. Start a totally new tradition this year – something that the three (or more) of you will do this holiday and then make it a lifelong family ritual.\r\n\r\nDon’t forget that travelling with baby is much more complicated than just taking an extra bag. Babies can get overwhelmed by too many changes to their routines and surroundings, be prepared and bring some of their comforts from home.'),
(2708, 290, '_page_module_4_content_left', 'field_5c866f3d4f1a5'),
(2709, 290, 'page_module_4_image_right', '152'),
(2710, 290, '_page_module_4_image_right', 'field_5c866f444f1a6'),
(2711, 290, 'page_module_4_content_right', '<h3><strong>1 MONTH</strong>\r\nFirst Outing</h3>\r\nThe time has come to venture out of your cozy nest for the first time with your precious little one. The days of leaving the apartment in 5 minutes flat, squeezing in a trip to the bank and dropping by the grocery store for a quick errand are long gone. Be realistic and practical – factor in time for packing all the essentials, feedings, placing baby in the car seat, stowing and reopening the stroller and diaper changes.\r\n\r\nMake this very memorable milestone easier with a little thoughtful preparation and a few words of advice from been-there, done-that parents.'),
(2712, 290, '_page_module_4_content_right', 'field_5c866f4b4f1a7'),
(2713, 290, 'page_module_5_anchor_text', '4 - 6 MONTHS'),
