(3003, 303, 'page_module_4_content_right', '<h3><strong>1 MONTH</strong>\r\nFirst Outing</h3>\r\nThe time has come to venture out of your cozy nest for the first time with your precious little one. The days of leaving the apartment in 5 minutes flat, squeezing in a trip to the bank and dropping by the grocery store for a quick errand are long gone. Be realistic and practical – factor in time for packing all the essentials, feedings, placing baby in the car seat, stowing and reopening the stroller and diaper changes.\r\n\r\nMake this very memorable milestone easier with a little thoughtful preparation and a few words of advice from been-there, done-that parents.'),
(3004, 303, '_page_module_4_content_right', 'field_5c866f4b4f1a7'),
(3005, 303, 'page_module_5_anchor_text', '4 - 6 MONTHS'),
